;c m&aacute;y in từ bất cứ nơi n&agrave;o tr&ecirc;n thế giới.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>TH&Ocirc;NG SỐ KỸ THUẬT</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* &nbsp;C&ocirc;ng nghệ in: <strong>Truyền nhiệt trực tiếp v&agrave; gi&aacute;n tiếp</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* &nbsp;Độ ph&acirc;n giải: <strong>203dpi / 300 dpi </strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* Tốc độ in tối đa: <strong>14 ips (356mm /sec)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* Bề rộng nh&atilde;n tối đa c&oacute; thể in: <strong>6.6&rsquo;&rsquo;/168 mm</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* Chiều d&agrave;i nh&atilde;n tối đa c&oacute; thể in: <strong>102&rsquo;&rsquo; (2591 mm)/ &nbsp;45&rsquo;&rsquo; (1143 mm)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* Bộ nhớ: <strong>512MB Flash ,256MB SDRAM</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* Cổng giao tiếp: <strong>RS-232, USB, Ethernet</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">* K&iacute;ch thước: <strong>366.55x324x495mm (WxHxL)</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>T&Agrave;I LIỆU</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\">Zebra ZT420 Spec&nbsp;Sheet</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><a href=\"https://www.zebra.com/content/dam/zebra/product-information/en-us/brochures-datasheets/industrial/zt400-datasheet-215-en-us.pdf\"><span style=\"color:#008080\">https://www.zebra.com/content/dam/zebra/product-information/en-us/brochures-datasheets